Optimal engagement
The Ministry of Foreign Affairs youth mainstreaming action plan is a good starting point for a positive diplomacy where it reaffirms that young people are an essential asset worth investing in –recognizes youth as a vital resource and integral stakeholder in the development process and a key determinant in shaping the Country’s future thus, the need to ensure optimal engagement and participation to be able to tap the immense creativity and energy of youth.



